e̹͡%ԁѡЁЁlúԱЁɽ䁡́ѡѡȁͽѽQЁeЁͅɥltٔѡЁٕѡѡ䁩ЁѡЁٕѡѡЁ́ѡȁ݅!lú́ȁѡ͔ݡѡ͔ݡаѡ͔ݡ͕ٔɍѡ͔ݡٔɥȁluѡ䁍ɕєѡхݡٔѽՍѡȁٕ̹1ٔ́ݥluѠ͵ɽ́ݥѠ́́ݥѠѕȹQɥѕЁɔݥ͕݅́luѕаԁeЁݕչѥԁЁȁЁɕ́х̸]luԁݕɔɸԁݕɔ她ٕ役ɽչԁ݅́͵1ٔȁͼѡЁluԁԝɔѡݡ́͵ٕ役ɽչԁ́她A͔͕ѡ́luѼѡ͔ݡͽѡѼԱѼѡ͔ݡٔѽՍȁ݅䁽ȁluѡȱѼѡ͔ݡԁ͵ݡԁɕ䁹бѼѡ͔ѡЁԁ͕ѡɥѕȁluѡ́ݡԁɔɕ䁑ݸѼѡ͔ݡԁ݅ЁѼЁѡ܁ѡЁԁɕєѡluȁɥ͡ԁeаeЁݽ䱹ѡݥѼԱԁݥЁlúЁѡչѼɥѕͽéݥѠѡ́ͅ́ɕѡltѡݽɐ5䁉ե䁥͕́́ѼͥЁɕЁluѡɅѡͅ5䁉ѡаѼ͕ѡɅݕɐluͥͥаѡ͔̰䁵ٕ́䁵䰁䁵хѱ丁͕݅́lt͡ձѼͽѡȁɥєͽѡQݕ啅́Ʌѽ䁑ܰ͡Ցlu䁙ͽѡйɥ䁍ѡՍ䁵䁅܁ѡ́ɔͅ䁙ȁlu9܁eȰЁ́ѡمѡݥɔɔչѡЁѡ͔ѡ́ɔѥ)չȁ͍ѡ՝ЁѼٔ͠Ё́ѡЁѡɕɽѠЁٕȁѡltЁѡɕ啅́ѕȰ́ɥѥյՑ䁙չѡЁ͸Ёɕ䁝ɽ܁luЁ͕́́ЁͼхQ͍ѡЁ݅ЁѼٕٔЁѼЁȁluȁٽѡ͍ɕѡ́ɥЁٕ݅́Յ䁥ɍѥluݡɅՅѥ䁥ѡѡɽаѕȁѽѡэ́ݕЁɽ͕䰁luЁ́ѡɽݸͭщ̰Ց䁙չ͕́ɕ䁍Ёɕȁ́luɅluQɔɔ́ݡԁ́ͽͼՍѡЁԁЁ݅ЁѼѡɽluȁɕ́՜ѡȁɕɕݡЁԁ݅ЁѼɕ흼ݡɔԁ݅ЁѼ퉔ݡЁlt݅ЁѼ͔ԁٔ䁽Ѽѡѡ́ԁ݅ЁѼ5luԁٔ՝́Ѽԁݕб՝ɥ́Ѽԁɽ՝ͽɽ܁Ѽluԁյ՝Ѽԁ Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in e̹͡%ԁѡЁЁlúԱЁɽ䁡́ѡѡȁͽѽQЁeЁͅɥltٔѡЁٕѡѡ䁩ЁѡЁٕѡѡЁ́ѡȁ݅!lú́ȁѡ͔ݡѡ͔ݡаѡ͔ݡ͕ٔɍѡ͔ݡٔɥȁluѡ䁍ɕєѡхݡٔѽՍѡȁٕ̹1ٔ́ݥluѠ͵ɽ́ݥѠ́́ݥѠѕȹQɥѕЁɔݥ͕݅́luѕаԁeЁݕչѥԁЁȁЁɕ́х̸]luԁݕɔɸԁݕɔ她ٕ役ɽչԁ݅́͵1ٔȁͼѡЁluԁԝɔѡݡ́͵ٕ役ɽչԁ́她A͔͕ѡ́luѼѡ͔ݡͽѡѼԱѼѡ͔ݡٔѽՍȁ݅䁽ȁluѡȱѼѡ͔ݡԁ͵ݡԁɕ䁹бѼѡ͔ѡЁԁ͕ѡɥѕȁluѡ́ݡԁɔɕ䁑ݸѼѡ͔ݡԁ݅ЁѼЁѡ܁ѡЁԁɕєѡluȁɥ͡ԁeаeЁݽ䱹ѡݥѼԱԁݥЁlúЁѡչѼɥѕͽéݥ those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? e̹͡%ԁѡЁЁlúԱЁɽ䁡́ѡѡȁͽѽQЁeЁͅɥltٔѡЁٕѡѡ䁩ЁѡЁٕѡѡЁ́ѡȁ݅!lú́ȁѡ͔ݡѡ͔ݡаѡ͔ݡ͕ٔɍѡ͔ݡٔɥȁluѡ䁍ɕєѡхݡٔѽՍѡȁٕ̹1ٔ́ݥluѠ͵ɽ́ݥѠ́́ݥѠѕȹQɥѕЁɔݥ͕݅́luѕаԁeЁݕչѥԁЁȁЁɕ́х̸]luԁݕɔɸԁݕɔ她ٕ役ɽչԁ݅́͵1ٔȁͼѡЁluԁԝɔѡݡ́͵ٕ役ɽչԁ́她A͔͕ѡ́luѼѡ͔ݡͽѡѼԱѼѡ͔ݡٔѽՍȁ݅䁽ȁluѡȱѼѡ͔ݡԁ͵ݡԁɕ䁹бѼѡ͔ѡЁԁ͕ѡɥѕȁluѡ́ݡԁɔɕ䁑ݸѼѡ͔ݡԁ݅ЁѼЁѡ܁ѡЁԁɕєѡluȁɥ͡ԁeаeЁݽ䱹ѡݥѼԱԁݥЁlúЁѡչѼɥѕͽéݥѠѡ́ͅ́ɕѡltѡݽɐ5䁉ե䁥͕́́ѼͥЁɕЁluѡɅѡͅ5䁉ѡаѼ͕ѡɅݕɐluͥͥаѡ͔̰䁵ٕ́䁵䰁䁵хѱ丁͕݅́lt͡ձѼͽѡȁɥєͽѡQݕ啅́Ʌѽ䁑ܰ͡Ցlu䁙ͽѡйɥ䁍ѡՍ䁵䁅܁ѡ́ɔͅ䁙ȁlu9܁eȰЁ́ѡمѡݥɔɔչѡЁѡ͔ѡ́ɔѥ)չȁ͍ѡ՝ЁѼٔ͠Ё́ѡЁѡɕɽѠЁٕȁѡltЁѡɕ啅́ѕȰ́ɥѥյՑ䁙չѡЁ͸Ёɕ䁝ɽ܁luЁ͕́́ЁͼхQ͍ѡЁ݅ЁѼٕٔЁѼЁȁluȁٽѡ͍ɕѡ́ɥЁٕ݅́Յ䁥ɍѥluݡɅՅѥ䁥ѡѡɽаѕȁѽѡэ́ݕЁɽ͕䰁luЁ́ѡɽݸͭщ̰Ց䁙չ͕́ɕ䁍Ёɕȁ́luɅluQɔɔ́ݡԁ́ͽͼՍѡЁԁЁ݅ЁѼѡɽluȁɕ́՜ѡȁɕɕݡЁԁ݅ЁѼɕ흼ݡɔԁ݅ЁѼ퉔ݡЁlt݅ЁѼ͔ԁٔ䁽Ѽѡѡ́ԁ݅ЁѼ5luԁٔ՝́Ѽԁݕб՝ɥ́Ѽԁɽ՝ͽɽ܁Ѽluԁյ՝Ѽԁ Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? e̹͡%ԁѡЁЁlúԱЁɽ䁡́ѡѡȁͽѽQЁeЁͅɥltٔѡЁٕѡѡ䁩ЁѡЁٕѡѡЁ́ѡȁ݅!lú́ȁѡ͔ݡѡ͔ݡаѡ͔ݡ͕ٔɍѡ͔ݡٔɥȁluѡ䁍ɕєѡхݡٔѽՍѡȁٕ̹1ٔ́ݥluѠ͵ɽ́ݥѠ́́ݥѠѕȹQɥѕЁɔݥ͕݅́luѕаԁeЁݕչѥԁЁȁЁɕ́х̸]luԁݕɔɸԁݕɔ她ٕ役ɽչԁ݅́͵1ٔȁͼѡЁluԁԝɔѡݡ́͵ٕ役ɽչԁ́她A͔͕ѡ́luѼѡ͔ݡͽѡѼԱѼѡ͔ݡٔѽՍȁ݅䁽ȁluѡȱѼѡ͔ݡԁ͵ݡԁɕ䁹бѼѡ͔ѡЁԁ͕ѡɥѕȁluѡ́ݡԁɔɕ䁑ݸѼѡ͔ݡԁ݅ЁѼЁѡ܁ѡЁԁɕєѡluȁɥ͡ԁeаeЁݽ䱹ѡݥѼԱԁݥЁlúЁѡչѼɥѕͽéݥѠѡ́ͅ́ɕѡltѡݽɐ5䁉ե䁥͕́́ѼͥЁɕЁluѡɅѡͅ5䁉ѡаѼ͕ѡɅݕɐluͥͥаѡ͔̰䁵ٕ́䁵䰁䁵хѱ丁͕݅́lt͡ձѼͽѡȁɥєͽѡQݕ啅́Ʌѽ䁑ܰ͡Ցlu䁙ͽѡйɥ䁍ѡՍ䁵䁅܁ѡ́ɔͅ䁙ȁlu9܁eȰЁ́ѡمѡݥɔɔչѡЁѡ͔ѡ́ɔѥ)չȁ͍ѡ՝ЁѼٔ͠Ё́ѡЁѡɕɽѠЁٕȁѡltЁѡɕ啅́ѕȰ́ɥѥյՑ䁙չѡЁ͸Ёɕ䁝ɽ܁luЁ͕́́ЁͼхQ͍ѡЁ݅ЁѼٕٔЁѼЁȁluȁٽѡ͍ɕѡ́ɥЁٕ݅́Յ䁥ɍѥluݡɅՅѥ䁥ѡѡɽаѕȁѽѡэ́ݕЁɽ͕䰁luЁ́ѡɽݸͭщ̰Ց䁙չ͕́ɕ䁍Ёɕȁ́luɅluQɔɔ́ݡԁ́ͽͼՍѡЁԁЁ݅ЁѼѡɽluȁɕ́՜ѡȁɕɕݡЁԁ݅ЁѼɕ흼ݡɔԁ݅ЁѼ퉔ݡЁlt݅ЁѼ͔ԁٔ䁽Ѽѡѡ́ԁ݅ЁѼ5luԁٔ՝́Ѽԁݕб՝ɥ́Ѽԁɽ՝ͽɽ܁Ѽluԁյ՝Ѽԁ Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? e̹͡%ԁѡЁЁlúԱЁɽ䁡́ѡѡȁͽѽQЁeЁͅɥltٔѡЁٕѡѡ䁩ЁѡЁٕѡѡЁ́ѡȁ݅!lú́ȁѡ͔ݡѡ͔ݡаѡ͔ݡ͕ٔɍѡ͔ݡٔɥȁluѡ䁍ɕєѡхݡٔѽՍѡȁٕ̹1ٔ́ݥluѠ͵ɽ́ݥѠ́́ݥѠѕȹQɥѕЁɔݥ͕݅́luѕаԁeЁݕչѥԁЁȁЁɕ́х̸]luԁݕɔɸԁݕɔ她ٕ役ɽչԁ݅́͵1ٔȁͼѡЁluԁԝɔѡݡ́͵ٕ役ɽչԁ́她A͔͕ѡ́luѼѡ͔ݡͽѡѼԱѼѡ͔ݡٔѽՍȁ݅䁽ȁluѡȱѼѡ͔ݡԁ͵ݡԁɕ䁹бѼѡ͔ѡЁԁ͕ѡɥѕȁluѡ́ݡԁɔɕ䁑ݸѼѡ͔ݡԁ݅ЁѼЁѡ܁ѡЁԁɕєѡluȁɥ͡ԁeаeЁݽ䱹ѡݥѼԱԁݥЁlúЁѡչѼɥѕͽéݥѠѡ́ͅ́ɕѡltѡݽɐ5䁉ե䁥͕́́ѼͥЁɕЁluѡɅѡͅ5䁉ѡаѼ͕ѡɅݕɐluͥͥаѡ͔̰䁵ٕ́䁵䰁䁵хѱ丁͕݅́lt͡ձѼͽѡȁɥєͽѡQݕ啅́Ʌѽ䁑ܰ͡Ցlu䁙ͽѡйɥ䁍ѡՍ䁵䁅܁ѡ́ɔͅ䁙ȁlu9܁eȰЁ́ѡمѡݥɔɔչѡЁѡ͔ѡ́ɔѥ)չȁ͍ѡ՝ЁѼٔ͠Ё́ѡЁѡɕɽѠЁٕȁѡltЁѡɕ啅́ѕȰ́ɥѥյՑ䁙չѡЁ͸Ёɕ䁝ɽ܁luЁ͕́́ЁͼхQ͍ѡЁ݅ЁѼٕٔЁѼЁȁluȁٽѡ͍ɕѡ́ɥЁٕ݅́Յ䁥ɍѥluݡɅՅѥ䁥ѡѡɽаѕȁѽѡэ́ݕЁɽ͕䰁luЁ́ѡɽݸͭщ̰Ց䁙չ͕́ɕ䁍Ёɕȁ́luɅluQɔɔ́ݡԁ́ͽͼՍѡЁԁЁ݅ЁѼѡɽluȁɕ́՜ѡȁɕɕݡЁԁ݅ЁѼɕ흼ݡɔԁ݅ЁѼ퉔ݡЁlt݅ЁѼ͔ԁٔ䁽Ѽѡѡ́ԁ݅ЁѼ5luԁٔ՝́Ѽԁݕб՝ɥ́Ѽԁɽ՝ͽɽ܁Ѽluԁյ՝Ѽԁ Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? e̹͡%ԁѡЁЁlúԱЁɽ䁡́ѡѡȁͽѽQЁeЁͅɥltٔѡЁٕѡѡ䁩ЁѡЁٕѡѡЁ́ѡȁ݅!lú́ȁѡ͔ݡѡ͔ݡаѡ͔ݡ͕ٔɍѡ͔ݡٔɥȁluѡ䁍ɕєѡхݡٔѽՍѡȁٕ̹1ٔ́ݥluѠ͵ɽ́ݥѠ́́ݥѠѕȹQɥѕЁɔݥ͕݅́luѕаԁeЁݕչѥԁЁȁЁɕ́х̸]luԁݕɔɸԁݕɔ她ٕ役ɽչԁ݅́͵1ٔȁͼѡЁluԁԝɔѡݡ́͵ٕ役ɽչԁ́她A͔͕ѡ́luѼѡ͔ݡͽѡѼԱѼѡ͔ݡٔѽՍȁ݅䁽ȁluѡȱѼѡ͔ݡԁ͵ݡԁɕ䁹бѼѡ͔ѡЁԁ͕ѡɥѕȁluѡ́ݡԁɔɕ䁑ݸѼѡ͔ݡԁ݅ЁѼЁѡ܁ѡЁԁɕєѡluȁɥ͡ԁeаeЁݽ䱹ѡݥѼԱԁݥЁlúЁѡչѼɥѕͽéݥѠѡ́ͅ́ɕѡltѡݽɐ5䁉ե䁥͕́́ѼͥЁɕЁluѡɅѡͅ5䁉ѡаѼ͕ѡɅݕɐluͥͥаѡ͔̰䁵ٕ́䁵䰁䁵хѱ丁͕݅́lt͡ձѼͽѡȁɥєͽѡQݕ啅́Ʌѽ䁑ܰ͡Ցlu䁙ͽѡйɥ䁍ѡՍ䁵䁅܁ѡ́ɔͅ䁙ȁlu9܁eȰЁ́ѡمѡݥɔɔչѡЁѡ͔ѡ́ɔѥ)չȁ͍ѡ՝ЁѼٔ͠Ё́ѡЁѡɕɽѠЁٕȁѡltЁѡɕ啅́ѕȰ́ɥѥյՑ䁙չѡЁ͸Ёɕ䁝ɽ܁luЁ͕́́ЁͼхQ͍ѡЁ݅ЁѼٕٔЁѼЁȁluȁٽѡ͍ɕѡ́ɥЁٕ݅́Յ䁥ɍѥluݡɅՅѥ䁥ѡѡɽаѕȁѽѡэ́ݕЁɽ͕䰁luЁ́ѡɽݸͭщ̰Ց䁙չ͕́ɕ䁍Ёɕȁ́luɅluQɔɔ́ݡԁ́ͽͼՍѡЁԁЁ݅ЁѼѡɽluȁɕ́՜ѡȁɕɕݡЁԁ݅ЁѼɕ흼ݡɔԁ݅ЁѼ퉔ݡЁlt݅ЁѼ͔ԁٔ䁽Ѽѡѡ́ԁ݅ЁѼ5luԁٔ՝́Ѽԁݕб՝ɥ́Ѽԁɽ՝ͽɽ܁Ѽluԁյ՝Ѽԁ Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? e̹͡%ԁѡЁЁlúԱЁɽ䁡́ѡѡȁͽѽQЁeЁͅɥltٔѡЁٕѡѡ䁩ЁѡЁٕѡѡЁ́ѡȁ݅!lú́ȁѡ͔ݡѡ͔ݡаѡ͔ݡ͕ٔɍѡ͔ݡٔɥȁluѡ䁍ɕєѡхݡٔѽՍѡȁٕ̹1ٔ́ݥluѠ͵ɽ́ݥѠ́́ݥѠѕȹQɥѕЁɔݥ͕݅́luѕаԁeЁݕչѥԁЁȁЁɕ́х̸]luԁݕɔɸԁݕɔ她ٕ役ɽչԁ݅́͵1ٔȁͼѡЁluԁԝɔѡݡ́͵ٕ役ɽչԁ́她A͔͕ѡ́luѼѡ͔ݡͽѡѼԱѼѡ͔ݡٔѽՍȁ݅䁽ȁluѡȱѼѡ͔ݡԁ͵ݡԁɕ䁹бѼѡ͔ѡЁԁ͕ѡɥѕȁluѡ́ݡԁɔɕ䁑ݸѼѡ͔ݡԁ݅ЁѼЁѡ܁ѡЁԁɕєѡluȁɥ͡ԁeаeЁݽ䱹ѡݥѼԱԁݥЁlúЁѡչѼɥѕͽéݥѠѡ́ͅ́ɕѡltѡݽɐ5䁉ե䁥͕́́ѼͥЁɕЁluѡɅѡͅ5䁉ѡаѼ͕ѡɅݕɐluͥͥаѡ͔̰䁵ٕ́䁵䰁䁵хѱ丁͕݅́lt͡ձѼͽѡȁɥєͽѡQݕ啅́Ʌѽ䁑ܰ͡Ցlu䁙ͽѡйɥ䁍ѡՍ䁵䁅܁ѡ́ɔͅ䁙ȁlu9܁eȰЁ́ѡمѡݥɔɔչѡЁѡ͔ѡ́ɔѥ)չȁ͍ѡ՝ЁѼٔ͠Ё́ѡЁѡɕɽѠЁٕȁѡltЁѡɕ啅́ѕȰ́ɥѥյՑ䁙չѡЁ͸Ёɕ䁝ɽ܁luЁ͕́́ЁͼхQ͍ѡЁ݅ЁѼٕٔЁѼЁȁluȁٽѡ͍ɕѡ́ɥЁٕ݅́Յ䁥ɍѥluݡɅՅѥ䁥ѡѡɽаѕȁѽѡэ́ݕЁɽ͕䰁luЁ́ѡɽݸͭщ̰Ց䁙չ͕́ɕ䁍Ёɕȁ́luɅluQɔɔ́ݡԁ́ͽͼՍѡЁԁЁ݅ЁѼѡɽluȁɕ́՜ѡȁɕɕݡЁԁ݅ЁѼɕ흼ݡɔԁ݅ЁѼ퉔ݡЁlt݅ЁѼ͔ԁٔ䁽Ѽѡѡ́ԁ݅ЁѼ5luԁٔ՝́Ѽԁݕб՝ɥ́Ѽԁɽ՝ͽɽ܁Ѽluԁյ՝Ѽԁ Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? e̹͡%ԁѡЁЁlúԱЁɽ䁡́ѡѡȁͽѽQЁeЁͅɥltٔѡЁٕѡѡ䁩ЁѡЁٕѡѡЁ́ѡȁ݅!lú́ȁѡ͔ݡѡ͔ݡаѡ͔ݡ͕ٔɍѡ͔ݡٔɥȁluѡ䁍ɕєѡхݡٔѽՍѡȁٕ̹1ٔ́ݥluѠ͵ɽ́ݥѠ́́ݥѠѕȹQɥѕЁɔݥ͕݅́luѕаԁeЁݕչѥԁЁȁЁɕ́х̸]luԁݕɔɸԁݕɔ她ٕ役ɽչԁ݅́͵1ٔȁͼѡЁluԁԝɔѡݡ́͵ٕ役ɽչԁ́她A͔͕ѡ́luѼѡ͔ݡͽѡѼԱѼѡ͔ݡٔѽՍȁ݅䁽ȁluѡȱѼѡ͔ݡԁ͵ݡԁɕ䁹бѼѡ͔ѡЁԁ͕ѡɥѕȁluѡ́ݡԁɔɕ䁑ݸѼѡ͔ݡԁ݅ЁѼЁѡ܁ѡЁԁɕєѡluȁɥ͡ԁeаeЁݽ䱹ѡݥѼԱԁݥЁlúЁѡչѼɥѕͽéݥѠѡ́ͅ́ɕѡltѡݽɐ5䁉ե䁥͕́́ѼͥЁɕЁluѡɅѡͅ5䁉ѡаѼ͕ѡɅݕɐluͥͥаѡ͔̰䁵ٕ́䁵䰁䁵хѱ丁͕݅́lt͡ձѼͽѡȁɥєͽѡQݕ啅́Ʌѽ䁑ܰ͡Ցlu䁙ͽѡйɥ䁍ѡՍ䁵䁅܁ѡ́ɔͅ䁙ȁlu9܁eȰЁ́ѡمѡݥɔɔչѡЁѡ͔ѡ́ɔѥ)չȁ͍ѡ՝ЁѼٔ͠Ё́ѡЁѡɕɽѠЁٕȁѡltЁѡɕ啅́ѕȰ́ɥѥյՑ䁙չѡЁ͸Ёɕ䁝ɽ܁luЁ͕́́ЁͼхQ͍ѡЁ݅ЁѼٕٔЁѼЁȁluȁٽѡ͍ɕѡ́ɥЁٕ݅́Յ䁥ɍѥluݡɅՅѥ䁥ѡѡɽаѕȁѽѡэ́ݕЁɽ͕䰁luЁ́ѡɽݸͭщ̰Ց䁙չ͕́ɕ䁍Ёɕȁ́luɅluQɔɔ́ݡԁ́ͽͼՍѡЁԁЁ݅ЁѼѡɽluȁɕ́՜ѡȁɕɕݡЁԁ݅ЁѼɕ흼ݡɔԁ݅ЁѼ퉔ݡЁlt݅ЁѼ͔ԁٔ䁽Ѽѡѡ́ԁ݅ЁѼ5luԁٔ՝́Ѽԁݕб՝ɥ́Ѽԁɽ՝ͽɽ܁Ѽluԁյ՝Ѽԁ Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in others’shoes.If you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you happy? Always put yourself in you feel that it [6]hurts you,it probably hurts the other person, too.The happiest of people don’t necessarily[7] have the best of everything;they just make the most of everything that comes along their way.Happ[8]iness lies for those who cry,those who hurt, those who have searched,and those who have tried,for on[9]ly they can appreciate the importance of people who have touched their lives.Love begins wi[10]th a smile,grows with a kiss and ends with a tear.The brightest future will always be based on a for[11]gotten past, you can’t go on well in lifeuntil you let go of your past failures and heartaches. Whe[12]n you were born,you were crying and everyone around you was smiling.Live your life so that w[13]hen you die,you're the one who is smiling and everyone around you is crying. Please send this mess[14]age to those people who mean something to you,to those who have touched your life in one way or ano[15]ther,to those who make you smile when you really need it,to those that make you see the brighter s[16]ide of things when you are really down,to those who you want to let them know that you appreciate th[17]eir friendship.And if you don’t, don’t worry,nothing bad will happen to you,you will just m[18]iss out on the opportunity to brighten someone’s day with this message. Age has reached the end[19] of the beginning of a word. May be guilty in his seems to passing a lot of different life becam[20]e the appearance of the same day; May be back in the past, to oneself the paranoid weird belief di[21]sillusionment, these days, my mind has been very messy, in my mind constantly. Always feel oneself[22] should go to do something, or write something. Twenty years of life trajectory deeply shallow, sudd[23]enly feel something, do it.During my childhood, think lucky money and new clothes are necessary for [24]New Year, but as the advance of the age, will be more and more found that those things are optional; Junior high school, thought to have a crush on just means that the real growth, but over the[25] past three years later, his writing of alumni in peace, suddenly found that isn't really grow u[26]p, it seems is not so important; Then in high school, think don't want to give vent to out your inne[27]r voice can be in the high school children of the feelings in a period, but was eventually infarctio[28]n when graduation party in the throat, later again stood on the pitch he has sweat profusely, look[29]ed at his thrown a basketball hoops, suddenly found himself has already can't remember his [30]appearance.[1]There are moments in life when you miss someone so much that you just want to pick them from [2]your dreams and hug them for real! Dream what you want to dream;go where you want to go;be what you[3] want to be,because you have only one life and one chance to do all the things you want to do.May yo[4]u have enough happiness to make you sweet,enough trials to make you strong,enough sorrow to keep [5]you human,enough hope to make you
